<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_266_r1l17"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wır <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . <expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Reıkarcʒhof<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l18"><expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Goldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . den wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l19"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu reden / von der ſcheden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dıe vns vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l20"><expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenern vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> etwıemengen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l21">
<del rend="strikethrough">enden beſchehen vnd ſunderlıch yecʒ neẅlıch von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l23">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan></del> cʒum Steın 
<add><ab facs="#facs_266_line_1577193100437_1899">newlıch </ab></add> beſchehen ſeyn Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l24">mıt fleıſſ . was <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r1l25">von <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade werben daʒ Jr ſıe darinn </ab>
