</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_266" id="132r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Ludweig<ex>en</ex></expan> von Peyern und
                                <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> czu Mortani etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Reikarczhof<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Goldlein, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, den wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu reden von der scheden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die uns und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienern und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        czum Stein <add>newlich</add> beschehen seyn. Und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
                        mit fleiss, was <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal in
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gnade werben, daz ir sie darinn <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn,
                        in des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                            <expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan></add> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
